Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:22.54,InsCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)\3c7DC621\an9\fs40}如果失去自信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:25.54,InsJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)\3c7DC621\an9\fs50\bord3}ひろって（届けよう）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:25.54,InsCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)\3c7DC621\an9\fs40}无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:28.50,InsJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)\3c7DC621\an9\fs50\bord3}いつでも（わたしがねっ！）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:28.50,InsCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)\3c7DC621\an9\fs40}我都会帮你找回的喔！
