Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\fnB5A3MBW9}我们5个人一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\fnB5A3MBW9\1aFF\t(350,120,\1a00)}恭候各位光临
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,恭候各位光临
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,日本最大的活动…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.61,0:19:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的舞台还真小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这才有我们的风格嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,无论何时何地都付出全力！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 紧张也是彩的伙伴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 伸出手来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要围成圈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,彩 交给你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,丸之山上缤纷彩…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel * Palettes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,武士道！
