Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:53.70,InsJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)\3c7DC621}さなぎのまま　閉じこめた羽根
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:56.18,InsCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)\3c7DC621}唱不出来 心放不开
